      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SWIFT DOMINO (8) quickly into stride and found the front, leading until late when third (23.71) at this track in a Restricted WIN over 410m. Won at her only start from this box. Rates highly and will give a great sight. ASSASSINATOR (2) has a terrific record this trip with two wins and three placings from five starts. Was out of placings last time (30.89) at The Meadows in a Grade 5, finishing seventh and beaten 14 lengths. Looks well placed here and among the chances. SIR EASY (7) got around the 400m at Warragul to take a Mix 6/7 in a sharp 22.75 for a 1.5 lengths success. Top win latest and rates a key player again. ELMA'S GIRL (1) placed last time and cannot be ignored.",
